    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit. This high-revving inline-six utilizes six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power curve up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and transmitted to the tarmac via a speed-sensitive variable M-Differential Lock. The chassis maintains high torsional rigidity, supported by a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. While the aesthetic reflects honest use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp. Recent oil analysis confirms healthy rod bearing clearances. A mechanically robust example for the purist seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
